      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm working on a wellness program for some execs at a big firm. they want some tips on grooming and how they should present themselves to look more authoritative and professional during high-stakes boardroom meetings. can u give me some general guidance on what they should aim for?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
