      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. i guess i'm looking for more specifics though. like, when you say \"neatly\" for hair or \"subtle\" for makeup, how does that actually look in practice? i want to make sure i'm giving them concrete examples so there's no confusion about what looks \"distracting\" vs what looks \"professional.\"",
