      "content": "thanks. one thing i'm thinking about is the hair. some of my clients have more natural textures, like braids, locs, or very curly/coily hair. how should they approach that to make sure they fit this \"neat\" and \"professional\" vibe you're talking about without it being seen as a distraction?",
